cscie97.asn4.knowledge.engine

Class QueryEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn4.knowledge.engine.QueryEngine

  • public class QueryEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    Supports the execution of KnowledgeGraph queries. Queries are in the N-Triple format. The "?" represents a wild card in the query. All matching results are printed out.
